    • Method Detail

      • fill

        public static boolean fill(Context context,
                           int resourceStringArray,
                           Spinner spinner)
        Fills a Spinner object with an array of strings that exists somewhere in a resource xml file.
        Parameters:
        context - A reference to the Activity that the spinner exists in.
        resourceStringArray - An integer that points to a resource that holds an array of strings. Two examples of this are in app/res/values/strings.xml, near the bottom.
        spinner - A reference to the Spinner object that you want to populate with the string array resource.
        Returns:
        Whether or not the fill operation succeeded. Right now, it only returns true; I haven't yet figured out how to detect a failure.
